<br>
Have a druid harmony him while you move people in place.  Line up melees on left wall in his room, put nuke casters on left side of entrance doorway.  Your main tank (56+ warrior with ripo disc &amp; chain runed) charges it and engages ripo disc, turning to expose it's back to the others, then calls assist and all the other melees charge and the casters nuke.  All melees should use their best fast damage discipline (duelist, mightystrike, fellstrike, etc) except the MT (using ripo disc).<br>
